com.facebook.buck.rules

Class CellFilesystemResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.CellFilesystemResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function<Optional<java.lang.String>,ProjectFilesystem>

    public class CellFilesystemResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements Function<Optional<java.lang.String>,ProjectFilesystem>
    Provides a mechanism to take the cell name from a BuildTarget and resolve that down to a ProjectFilesystem.

    This is used to provide a layer of indirection from Cell to TargetGraphToActionGraph without needing to make everything aware of how to handle Cells. Equality is measured by comparing the underlying filesystems, since this is how we manage equality of Cell instances.
